{"id":27470355166,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGZVxa3g","head_branch":"DHIS2-21617-async-cdsr-import-new-period","head_sha":"f20519f6213dbef11a69b17813a37514a115993f","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54168,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"DHIS2-21617 Always commit new periods when mixing transactions","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":73914308734,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAARNaLYfg","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166","created_at":"2026-06-13T15:04:15Z","updated_at":"2026-06-13T15:12:42Z","run_started_at":"2026-06-13T15:04:15Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/73914308734","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27470355166/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"refactor: single transaction-strategy decision point, strict join path\n\nPreviously save() called runAutoJoinTransaction, which itself decided\njoin-vs-new - so \"choosing autojoin\" could still end up in a new\ntransaction. Move that decision into one dispatcher, runInTransaction,\nwhich is the only place that branches on the ambient transaction state:\n\n- joinActiveTransaction  : joins the caller's active read-write tx;\n                           throws if there is none (hard precondition)\n- runInNewTransaction    : commits in its own independent tx\n\nsave()/addPeriodType()/updatePeriodType() go through the dispatcher\n(they may be called with or without an active tx, e.g. a controller\ncalling reloadPeriod directly, so the new-tx fallback is required);\nreloadForceAddPeriodInNewTransaction() calls runInNewTransaction\ndirectly. The join path no longer silently falls back - it fails loud\nif entered without a transaction.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian-sandvold@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"f20519f6213dbef11a69b17813a37514a115993f","tree_id":"26ad60f0b8cb10e707e42815eb9fd53d72a46942","timestamp":"2026-06-13T15:04:09Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian-sandvold@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","a